{"tid":2077401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國穆斯林女孩面試被要求脫頭巾 拍片反歧視為個人權利發聲 超市其後聯絡道歉","createTime":"2020-06-24T09:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:34:02.000Z","uid":133680,"like":6,"dislike":129,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"58acfa7b73f6a2f2cbabc260e88f49a2d91650ef","tid":2077401,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205022&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=7f5e2740\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205022&h=4558c278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205022</a><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國非裔男之死點燃全球反種族歧視抗爭，世界各地都接連出現示威遊行，歧視議題也引起大眾熱議，德國近日傳出穆斯林女孩到超市面試，竟被主管要求脫下頭巾，遭歧視的經歷促使她拍片發聲。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，全球反歧視浪潮延燒，信仰伊斯蘭教的女學生米里安（Miriam J.）近日在IG上傳影片，分享被歧視的經歷，她指稱，自己到德國最大連鎖超市「艾德卡」（Edeka）應徵，被主管告知說「如果想要工作，就必須脫下頭巾」，讓她感受遭到種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n根據《世界報》報導，米里安在影片中淚訴「沒有人能要求我脫掉頭巾」，她要發聲為自己的權利而戰。艾德卡集團在影片發布後，已和米里安聯絡，向她鄭重道歉，並發布聲明表示，「反對各種形式的歧視，公司名稱代表多樣性，我們對員工不該要求出生，而是奉獻精神和社會融合」。"},{"pid":"216f70fd9cb2f56fc127fa345d4262cac725a005","tid":2077401,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CBAPxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CBAPxg.png&h=98afefc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OZKnuxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOZKnuxh.png&h=179d9449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ddecdaf5331f8c409047e405330983ffa3a0fcb","tid":2077401,"uid":68084,"like":83,"dislike":4,"score":79,"citedBy"