","tid":2077401,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"03191dead9b9afcb22c4e8f0db8e8fd4135fdba4","tid":2077401,"uid":133680,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"26e67239a6a3d95e72d8ddd9e6ba2db6f6a997f2","tid":2077401,"uid":21545,"like":38,"dislike":5,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:20:23.000Z","msg":"咁點解要佢除先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拎把錫克教刀Interview sin?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:59:16.000Z","msg":"拎錫克刀走街走都冇問題<br />\n係香港見過 第一次比佢嚇撚死"},{"pid":"1e12408120fd07372fdfde6390808868445acc6d","tid":2077401,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58acfa7b73f6a2f2cbabc260e88f49a2d91650ef","tid":2077401,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:04:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205022&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPkwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=7f5e2740\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3205022&h=4558c278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3205022</a><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國非裔男之死點燃全球反種族歧視抗爭，世界各地都接連出現示威遊行，歧視議題也引起大眾熱議，德國近日傳出穆斯林女孩到超市面試，竟被主管要求脫下頭巾，遭歧視的經歷促使她拍片發聲。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，全球反歧視浪潮延燒，信仰伊斯蘭教的女學生米里安（Miriam J.）近日在IG上傳影片，分享被歧視的經歷，她指稱，自己到德國最大連鎖超市「艾德卡」（Edeka）應徵，被主管告知說「如果想要工作，就必須脫下頭巾」，讓她感受遭到種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n根據《世界報》報導，米里安在影片中淚訴「沒有人能要求我脫掉頭巾」，她要發聲為自己的權利而戰。艾德卡集團在影片發布後，已和米里安聯絡，向她鄭重道歉，並發布聲明表示，「反對各種形式的歧視，公司名稱代表多樣性，我們對員工不該要求出生，而是奉獻精神和社會融合」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"幾靚囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a